-- EU Raises Hungary Budget Deficit Forecast, Portfolio.hu Says
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-03-09T06:33:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-09/eu-raises-hungary-budget-deficit-forecast-portfolio-hu-says.html
The European Commission increased
its forecast for Hungary’s budget deficit this year and next,
news website  portfolio.hu  reported, citing a commission
document.  The European Union’s executive arm raised the forecast for
the 2012 budget gap to 3 percent of gross domestic product from
2.75 percent and the projection for 2013 to 3.6 percent from
3.25 percent, portfolio.hu said late yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest at 
